    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your radiant power makes you resistant to disease, protecting you as you offer succor to the ill. You gain a +2 status bonus to saves against diseases and poisons and to flat checks to recover from persistent poison damage. Allies in your paladin's aura get this benefit, but their bonus is +1.</p><p>In addition, if you roll a success on a save against a disease or poison, you get a critical success instead. (Your allies don't share this benefit.) If you have the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.class-features.Item.VTHNgc2eNH1MTBli]{Fortified Warrior} class feature, when you roll a critical failure on a save against a disease or poison, you get a failure instead.</p>",
